- phase: 5
  id: polish
  title: "Fejlhåndtering og polish"
  milestone: "Produktionsklar proxy"
  delivers:
    - Crash-recovery (downstream dies → remove tools → list_changed) ✓
    - Graceful shutdown (SIGTERM/Ctrl+C handling) ✓
    - Configurable timeout (init_timeout_secs, tool_call_timeout_secs) ✓
    - Error resilience (exponential backoff, watcher cancellation) ✓
