- phase: 4
  id: config-and-restart
  title: "Config file + restart + watcher + logging + compartmentalization"
  milestone: "Auto-load servere fra config, restart ved crash/binary-ændring, struktureret logging, compartmentaliseret tool-liste"
  delivers:
    - mcp-servers.json config parser
    - Auto-load gui-mcp, rules, rulestools ved proxy start
    - mcp/load, mcp/unload, mcp/list, mcp/restart management tools
    - Binary file watcher (notify crate)
    - Auto-restart ved binary Modify event
    - Structured logging (tracing crate → mcp-proxy.log)
    - 5-second initialization timeout for slow Python servers
    - Compartmentalized mcp/list output (tools grouped by server_id)
  status: done

- phase: 1
  id: setup
  title: "Project setup"
  milestone: "Project scaffolded, builds, scans clean"
  delivers:
    - Project structure
