- phase: 3
  id: mcp-protocol
  title: "MCP protocol + multiplexer"
  milestone: "Proxy er selv en MCP-server, kan spawne og route til multiple downstream servere"
  delivers:
    - JSON-RPC parser (upstream read loop)
    - MCP initialize/tools_list/tools_call handlers
    - Downstream server registry (spawn, initialize, collect tools)
    - Tool routing: namespace prefix → downstream dispatch
    - mcp/load, mcp/unload, mcp/list, mcp/restart management tools
    - notifications/tools/list_changed upstream
  status: done

- phase: 2
  id: proxy-core
  title: "Stdio relay + supervisor"
  milestone: "Proxy relay'er stdin/stdout mellem Claude og downstream process"
  delivers:
    - ProcessGateway_gtw (spawn downstream)
    - RelayGateway_gtw (tokio::io::copy)
    - ProxyAdapter_adp (dual relay with tokio::join)
    - CLI arg parsing (binary path + args)
  status: done
